text: ONE DAY ONLY! The average life of a mercury thermostat is 20 years. Disposed incorrectly, mercury from old thermostats can cause damage to the human nervous system or the wildlife food chain. text:
It’s time for #springcleaning! Follow these tips for clean air and a clean home. 

-Use naturally based products.
-Avoid harsh chemicals during the hottest parts of the day.
-DIY supplies from simple ingredients like baking soda, vinegar and lemons.

#Knozone
text_html: It’s time for #springcleaning! Follow these tips for clean air and a clean home. -Use naturally based products. -Avoid harsh chemicals during the hottest parts of the day. -DIY supplies from simple ingredients like baking soda, vinegar and lemons. #Knozone
